WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: G1fAXwYPQN4

NOTE Language: en

00:00:07.933 --> 00:00:15.425
And so now we have to realize 
it has a very big symbol

00:00:15.505 --> 00:00:22.766
that we all have gathered 
to this great city of Rome.

00:00:34.346 --> 00:00:37.954
As I said, Europe is the liver.

00:00:38.034 --> 00:00:49.527
That means all the attention is in Europe.

00:00:56.845 --> 00:01:01.496
But the attention, if does not have the heart

00:01:01.576 --> 00:01:07.440
it is absolutely not integrated, 
nor it is enlightened.

00:01:15.279 --> 00:01:20.316
But when the heart is sleeping 
how to bring heart to the attention?

00:01:27.604 --> 00:01:31.084
But some tricks here and there played so well

00:01:31.164 --> 00:01:39.723
that the heart, like a lion, leaped 
and we are here.

00:02:07.984 --> 00:02:15.651
The joy of all the Sahaja Yogis 
 is now going to fill the attention

00:02:15.975 --> 00:02:20.452
and new powers will be developed 
for all of you

00:02:20.516 --> 00:02:25.508
and you will all feel responsible 
for spreading Sahaja Yoga.

00:02:36.647 --> 00:02:38.833
It has to happen.

00:02:51.916 --> 00:03:00.226
Thus we realize that through effort,

00:03:00.306 --> 00:03:04.736
we all can achieve the impossible.

00:03:15.168 --> 00:03:21.000
Brahmarandra is the heart, 
is the heart chakra.

00:03:25.744 --> 00:03:33.134
And unless and until there is heart into our work 
we are not enlightened people.

00:03:41.227 --> 00:03:45.576
All our efforts will be futile.

00:03:53.135 --> 00:03:56.821
Without the attention the heart is useless.

00:04:02.683 --> 00:04:13.176
So this beautiful meeting that has taken place 
is writing in the skies

00:04:13.713 --> 00:04:24.759
with the warmth of the heart 
and light of the attention,

00:04:38.323 --> 00:04:43.166
that the glorious days have come

00:04:43.246 --> 00:04:47.665
for us to enjoy our complete freedom,

00:04:57.496 --> 00:05:03.376
freedom from all our enemies, 
all our ignorance.
